sentence: What are the course prerequisites for EECS 281 ?
sentence-with-vars: What are the course prerequisites for department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias1.NAME , COURSEalias1.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN COURSE AS COURSEalias1 ON COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 281 ;

SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE AS COURSEalias1 , COURSE_PREREQUISITE AS COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.PRE_COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSE_PREREQUISITEalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 281 ;
